description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Chukcha purrs with a rating of 67, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 134, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Box for East, 2 for South, and 5 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30672-74251-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [134 Votes, Top 15% Score]
